Commentary: oh my god! Malik's been hit on the back of the head. This is scary to watch! He's batting without a helmet or a cap and he's been hit right in the back of the head. This one was looped across on middle, and Malik looked for a quick single after dropping it into the covers. He is sent back and turns around. Colin Munro runs in from the covers and swoops down on the ball. Picks it up and fires a throw and the ball hits Malik's head and rebounds off it before lobbing up and rebounding to the fine leg boundary. Yes, went all the way to the boundary after the deflection, so you can imagine how hard that must have been
